{"id": 3106, "genre": 1001, "title": "哪些小事让你意识到时代其实并没有变，本质上还是跟小时候一样？", "description": "很多事只是 1.0 和 2.0 版本的不同。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 2297, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191228222015wA9h6KixFurNamqR.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-12-28T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 351232, "content": "小时候不想上学盼着放假，长大了不想上班盼着放假", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1675938}, {"id": 351233, "content": "现在的做微商的同学和小时候卖安利的叔叔阿姨一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 107, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1318584}, {"id": 351238, "content": "ccv", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 620618}, {"id": 351239, "content": "历史咯，人性咯\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1490380}, {"id": 351241, "content": "现在的孩子往往跟小时候的我一样令人讨厌", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1212252}, {"id": 351242, "content": "我们老师说现在网红直播打赏就像以前的街上卖艺，只是形式不同，而且艺人地位也高了😁", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616073}, {"id": 351244, "content": "天冷了，给自己的孩子穿上了春秋衣春秋裤…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446637}, {"id": 351255, "content": "电视上一直有很占用时间的广告，一个广告很久，以前是直白的直销，现在打安全温情", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1123732}, {"id": 351256, "content": "一样没心没肺 哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1675963}, {"id": 351258, "content": "历史上的每件事都在重复", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1649131}, {"id": 351260, "content": "我看完这一集动画片就去写作业\n我看完这一集电视剧就去赶报价", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1244859}, {"id": 351262, "content": "庞氏骗局还在，只是换了层皮: 虚拟货币，球鞋……", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141452}, {"id": 351263, "content": "人类仍然生活在地球", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484388}, {"id": 352288, "content": "从小到大，一直在思考一个终极问题：真知何在？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680135}, {"id": 351267, "content": "现在有了微信红包之后，用红皮纸包红包的习俗仍在。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1381632}, {"id": 351268, "content": "喜欢吹牛逼的人还是那么多！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1598598}, {"id": 351529, "content": "吃喝拉撒睡", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952563}, {"id": 351283, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈看到结婚三件套第一反应房车户口，是这样吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855520}, {"id": 351539, "content": "依然在追梦", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676553}, {"id": 351284, "content": "2020年了还是没有满天飞的汽车", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676062}, {"id": 351286, "content": "欲望还是那点东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 132566}, {"id": 351287, "content": "看完罗宾汉，发现几百年了世道并没有变好\n过完这一年，发现 世风日下 人生艰难", "image": "img/option/option/20191231194431VPNTafIl01ruq7hY", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676116}, {"id": 351294, "content": "没有反思，必将重复", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1649080}, {"id": 352323, "content": "思想", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680555}, {"id": 351300, "content": "小时候没钱，比大多数人穷；长大了有钱了，还是比大多数人穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469748}, {"id": 352327, "content": "过年家庭聚会还是被使唤着给长辈问好倒水端菜", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1679287}, {"id": 351312, "content": "每次离开家时父母总会给我拿上一堆东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1443843}, {"id": 351571, "content": "  筷子没有实质的改变，中国人离不开筷子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676553}, {"id": 351318, "content": "小时候不想上学，说老师坏话。长大了不想上班，说老板坏话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676147}, {"id": 351319, "content": "教育体制还是没变", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1586215}, {"id": 352608, "content": "从小的时候认为做的好事，可能就是坏事，长大后以为做了坏事，有可能变为是好事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1630544}, {"id": 351334, "content": "小时候，班级里各种小圈子；长大后，社会上各种小圈子。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674979}, {"id": 351341, "content": "三驾马车", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1370315}, {"id": 351352, "content": "从前一箱CD 现在一堆硬盘", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555556}, {"id": 351354, "content": "小时候的朋友现在还是朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1416200}, {"id": 351369, "content": "，", "image": "img/option/option/202001021656206LqCthpjBMrPwTU1.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297776}, {"id": 351627, "content": "小时候大家看电视消遣，现在人们刷手机视频，自动播和自个滑的区别", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008716}, {"id": 352156, "content": "坏习惯还是没改", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1642571}, {"id": 351695, "content": "还是那么帅😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676926}, {"id": 351451, "content": "小时候以为长大社会不会歧视大龄未婚女性，没想到现在很多人还是觉得女性随着岁月一天天在贬值", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676339}, {"id": 351709, "content": "现在在steam上买游戏，不过就是小时候攒钱买些小玩具长大了攒钱买一些大玩具嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1661040}, {"id": 351457, "content": "嗦粉还是用搪瓷碗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674050}, {"id": 351206, "content": "小时候第一时间接老师的话茬，长大了博主底下抢热评抢首赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 71, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351207, "content": "小时候买干脆面集卡片，长大了买盲盒", "image": null, "praise_count": 266, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351208, "content": "以前旅游喜欢刻“到此一游”，现在在弹幕上“火钳刘明”", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351209, "content": "在淘宝上看直播，跟以前看电视购物一回事嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 436, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 351465, "content": "还是那么穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1676378}, {"id": 351211, "content": "我爸还是我爸，我哥们还是我哥们，我老师还是我老师，我的个性还是我的个性，我的理想还是我的理想", "image": null, "praise_count": 57, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665111}, {"id": 351213, "content": "大家都还住在地上", "image": null, "praise_count": 123, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1373628}, {"id": 351214, "content": "大家也还开着在地上跑的车。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1347494}]}